{
  "texts": [
    "From the gathered articles, 500 sentences were randomly chosen.",
    "Economic experts from Canada's central bank labelled the dataset.",
    "The economists provided hierarchical labels for these sampled sentences.",
    "At the first level, sentences were labelled \"Relevant\" or \"Not Relevant\" to oil commodities.",
    "The next level subset \"Relevant\" sentences into one or more of \"Prices Positive,\" \"Prices Negative,\" \"Supply Positive,\" \"Supply Negative,\" \"Demand Positive,\" or \"Demand Negative\" for the oil commodity."
  ]
}